{"tid":1654330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐達禮明年9月約滿後不再續任證監會行政總裁","createTime":"2019-10-14T14:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T14:41:12.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f96319945c033a92bb4ce1b81b0dd8168c022b4b","tid":1654330,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"證監會說，歐達禮出任總裁8年，任內為處理市場風險，將證監會建設成堅強、稱職及有效率的監管機構，積極推行多項政策及行動上的改革；有關改革推行後已經到位及制度化，歐達禮認為目前是合適時間過渡至新領導層。<br />\n<br />\n外電較早時報道，歐達禮在今日證監會內部通訊中公布決定。政府將為行政總裁人選進行全球招聘。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486146-20191014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486146-20191014.htm&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm98kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=2830dcd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486146-20191014.htm&h=a39625a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486146-20191014.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e98e7e227544fe04a23bb9bcbb7ae5c60a521080","tid":1654330,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:18:21.000Z","msg":"回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c331fd4a1a922b7e4ed3c848967a5a135f022f","tid":1654330,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"證監換人咁大單嘢無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}